Ext.data.JsonP['Maps']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Maps</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-41845752\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Maps</h1>\n    <p>Demonstrates how to use the Maps module and display annotations on iOS and Android.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox admonition admonition-info aui-message hint shadowed information-macro has-no-icon\">\n            <div class=\"title\">App Folder Location</div>\n            <p>alloy/test/apps/<strong class=\" \">ui/map</strong>    </p>\n    </div>\n        <p>Android and iOS applications use the <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Modules.Map\">Ti.Maps</a> add-on module, which is included with Titanium SDK, but needs to be added as a dependency to your project&apos;s tiapp.xml file.    </p>\n    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/41845752/ios.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/41845752/ios.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"250\">\n        </img></p>\n    <p>To use the Ti.Map module in your iOS or Android project you need to declare your module in the tiapp.xml file:    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">app/tiapp.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"app/tiapp.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;modules&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;module platform=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;iphone&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;ti.map&lt;/module&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;module platform=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;android&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;ti.map&lt;/module&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/modules&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <p>Alternatively, you add the module to your project by clicking the green     <img src=\"images/s/en_GB/5637/e1ef10868e8fe2f234a1a0b171b01cde1d9717c4.31/_/images/icons/emoticons/add.png\" alt=\"images/s/en_GB/5637/e1ef10868e8fe2f234a1a0b171b01cde1d9717c4.31/_/images/icons/emoticons/add.png\" class=\"emoticon emoticon-plus\">\n in the Module section of the tiapp.xml overview screen, selecting the <strong class=\" \">ti.map</strong> module in the Mobile Modules dialog, and clicking OK.    </img></p>\n    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/41845752/map_add.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/41845752/map_add.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"350\">\n        </img></p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-41845752_Maps-Androidsetup\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Android setup</span></h2>\n    <p>To use the Maps module on Android, there are some setup tasks you first need to complete:    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link unresolved\" href=\"#!/guide/Maps-section-src-41845752\">Install the Google Play Services SDK</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link unresolved\" href=\"#!/guide/Maps-section-src-41845752\">Obtain and Add a Google API Key</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link unresolved\" href=\"#!/guide/Maps-section-src-41845752\">Obtain the SHA-1 certificate fingerprint</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link unresolved\" href=\"#!/guide/Maps-section-src-41845752\">Add the Google API key and permissions to the tiapp.xml file</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>Once these steps are complete, using the Map module is the same on Android or iOS.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-41845752_Maps-AppConfiguration\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>App Configuration</span></h2>\n    <p>As shown in the sample, app to use the Map module on iOS or Android, add a <tt class=\" \">&lt;Module/&gt;</tt> element to your XML view with its <strong class=\" \"><tt class=\" \">module</tt></strong> attribute set to &quot;<strong class=\" \">ti.map</strong>&quot;. The sample app also declares several &lt;Annotation/&gt; elements with named &quot;id&quot; attributes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">app/views/index.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"app/views/index.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t&lt;Window </code><code class=\"keyword\">class</code><code class=\"plain\">=</code><code class=\"string\">&apos;container&apos;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    \t&lt;Module id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;map&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> module=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;ti.map&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> method=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;createView&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;!-- annotation styled via tss file --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;Annotation id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;annotation1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;!-- annotation styles via inline style --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;Annotation title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Palo Alto&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> latitude=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;37.47&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> longitude=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;-122.12&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;!-- platform-specific annotations --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;Annotation id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;annotation2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> platform=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;android&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;Annotation id=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;annotation3&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> platform=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;ios&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;!-- annotation via &lt;Require&gt; tag --&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;Require src=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;annotationView&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Sunnyvale&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> latitude=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;37.37&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> longitude=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;-122.03&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;!--</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t\tLets add a UI component to show Annotations being declared</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t    side-by-side with child components. Map subviews will appear</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t    on iOS only.</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t--&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t\t&lt;Require src=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;overlay&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> platform=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;ios&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t\t&lt;/Module&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">\t&lt;/Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <p>The index.tss file assigns values to properties of the Map object, and to the Annotation objects defined in the XML view.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">app/styles/index.tss</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"app/styles/index.tss\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"string\">&quot;.container&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    backgroundColor:</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;white&quot;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">},</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"string\">&quot;#map&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    region: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        latitude: </code><code class=\"value\">37.38</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        latitudeDelta: </code><code class=\"value\">0.2</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        longitude: -</code><code class=\"value\">122.05</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        longitudeDelta: </code><code class=\"value\">0.2</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    },</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    mapType: Alloy.Globals.Map.SATELLITE_TYPE</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">},</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"string\">&quot;#annotation1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    title:</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Mountain View&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    latitude:</code><code class=\"value\">37.389569</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    longitude:-</code><code class=\"value\">122.050212</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">},</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"string\">&quot;#annotation2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    title:</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Google HQ&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    latitude:</code><code class=\"value\">37.4231054</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    longitude:-</code><code class=\"value\">122.0823988</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">},</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"string\">&quot;#annotation3&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">: {</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    title:</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Apple HQ&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    latitude:</code><code class=\"value\">37.3308525</code><code class=\"plain\">,</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    longitude:-</code><code class=\"value\">122.0296837</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">}</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-41845752_Maps-SeeAlso\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>See Also</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/guide/Google_Maps_v2_for_Android\">Google Maps v2 for Android</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/guide/iOS_Map_Kit\">iOS Map Kit</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Native_Maps_and_Annotations\">Native Maps and Annotations</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>    </p>\n    <p>    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=41845752\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Maps"});